        "rich_text_bhGzpc": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Rich Text ",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Gen Z shoppers often look for things that feel individual and meaningful. Instead of following fast-changing trends, they prefer jewellery that reflects personality.</p><p>Vintage-style rings naturally offer that sense of individuality.</p><p>For example, the Round Solitaire Vintage Engagement Ring has a familiar solitaire design, but the setting adds small vintage touches that give it character. It doesn’t look like every other engagement ring you see.</p><p>This balance between simplicity and personality makes vintage rings appealing to people who want something distinctive.</p>",
            "custom_id": "styling-a-solitaire",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_7tGFcR": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Vintage Designs Work Beautifully With Modern Diamonds",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Vintage Designs Work Beautifully With Modern Diamonds</h2>",
            "custom_id": "vintage-designs",
            "text_alignment": "center"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_Qy6Y3x": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Even though vintage rings look traditional, they pair perfectly with modern diamonds and materials.</p><p>Today’s jewellery makers often combine vintage aesthetics with modern technology and ethically sourced stones.</p><p>At Lucira Jewelry, vintage-inspired rings are crafted using IGI-certified lab-grown diamonds, offering the brilliance of modern diamonds while maintaining classic design elements.</p><p>This combination allows buyers to enjoy vintage charm without compromising on quality or sustainability.</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_qwTzXx": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "The Romance Behind Vintage Jewellery",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>The Romance Behind Vintage Jewellery</h2>",
            "custom_id": "the-romance",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "image_YyBkHJ": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Wearing_a_Solitaire_Ring_for_Weddings_and_Festive_Celebrations.jpg"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_jcDrNq": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Another reason vintage rings resonate with younger buyers is the feeling of romance they carry.</p><p>Many vintage designs are inspired by historical jewellery periods such as Victorian, Edwardian, or Art Deco styles. These eras focused on elegance and symbolism.</p><p>When someone wears a vintage-style ring, it often feels like wearing a small piece of history.</p><p>The Vintage Halo Oval Diamond Ring reflects this romantic aesthetic well. The halo around the oval diamond adds softness and charm, making the ring feel timeless rather than trendy.</p><p><a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/engagement-rings\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/engagement-rings\"> engagement rings </a>especially, this romantic quality matters.</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
