        "rich_text_mEE3FU": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Vintage Rings Stand Out in a World of Minimal Jewellery",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Vintage Rings Stand Out in a World of Minimal Jewellery</h2>",
            "custom_id": "vintage-rings-stand",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_htc4FK": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Minimal jewellery has been popular for a while, but many buyers are starting to look for pieces that feel more expressive.</p><p>Vintage rings offer that balance. They still feel elegant, but the detailing makes them stand out.</p><p>Designs like the Regency Bloom Diamond Ring show how vintage inspiration can add depth to a ring without making it feel overly ornate.</p><p>Instead of large, flashy stones, vintage rings often rely on thoughtful design details to create beauty.</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
