          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Why Vintage Rings Work Well for Engagements",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Why Vintage Rings Work Well for Engagements</h2>",
            "custom_id": "why-vintage-rings-work",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "image_CV378m": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Styling_a_Solitaire_Ring_for_Date_Nights_and_Evening_Plans.jpg"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_PA9wLd": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Vintage-inspired engagement rings have become especially popular among younger couples.</p><p>There are a few reasons for this:<br/>1.] The designs feel timeless rather than trendy<br/>2.] The details make the ring look unique<br/>3.] The style carries a sense of romance and history<br/><br/>The <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/solitaire-rings\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/solitaire-rings\">Round Solitaire </a>Vintage Engagement Ring from Lucira is a good example of how a classic solitaire can gain personality through vintage design elements.</p><p>Couples often like the idea that their ring feels special rather than something everyone else is wearing.</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_xH7CqU": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "The Lucira Approach to Vintage-Inspired Rings",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>The Lucira Approach to Vintage-Inspired Rings</h2><p>At <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Lucira Jewelry\">Lucira Jewelry</a>, vintage rings are designed with the goal of blending tradition with modern elegance.</p><p>Each piece is crafted to capture the charm of classic jewellery while ensuring it fits comfortably into modern lifestyles. Rings such as the Vintage Halo Oval Diamond Ring or the Regency Bloom Diamond Ring reflect this balance between heritage and contemporary design.</p><p>By using responsibly created diamonds and refined craftsmanship, Lucira brings vintage romance into the present day.</p>",
            "custom_id": "the-lucira",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        }
